{
  "page": "House Ferren",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Ferren</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Ferren.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Ferren.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/71/House_Ferren.svg/250px-House_Ferren.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/71/House_Ferren.svg/375px-House_Ferren.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/71/House_Ferren.svg/500px-House_Ferren.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nPer saltire, red and gold checks, a silver and black ferret on green<br />(<i>Per saltire chequy gules and or and vert, in each flank point a ferret argent and sable</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlord</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Ferren</b> is a noble house from the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>. They blazons their arms with per saltire, red and gold checks, a silver and black <a href=\"/index.php/Ferret_(mammal)\" title=\"Ferret (mammal)\">ferret</a> on green.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Their words are not known.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#House_Ferren_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Ferren at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Ferren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Ferren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The colors of House Ferren are spotted by <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> among the banners of <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>'s army as it leaves <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Ferren_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Ferren at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Ferren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Ferren at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Ferrens during the timespan of the events described in <a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>No member of the house has appeared yet.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Ferren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, Arya VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. Heraldry: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"htt